#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:1
msgid "E3100"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `invalid_mbti`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`invalid_mbti`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:5
msgid "The package interface file is invalid."
msgstr "包接口文件无效。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:7
msgid ""
"An `.mbti` file describes the public interface of a package. MoonBit "
"reports this error when the file cannot be parsed as a valid interface "
"file."
msgstr ""
"`.mbti` 文件描述包的公开接口。当该文件无法按有效接口文件解析时，MoonBit 会报"
"告此错误。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:12
#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:22
msgid "pkg.mbti"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:12
msgid ""
"package \"moonbit-community/E3100\"\n"
"\n"
"let value = 1\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "修改建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:19
msgid ""
"Regenerate the interface with `moon info`, or edit it so it contains "
"valid interface declarations."
msgstr ""
"请使用 `moon info` 重新生成接口，或者手动编辑它，使其包含有效的接口声明。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3100.md:22
msgid ""
"package \"moonbit-community/E3100-fixed\"\n"
"\n"
"fn value() -> Int\n"
msgstr ""

